<div class="app-card-container"> 
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <br>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 250, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img'%>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Hi, my name is Sashweana Rajendran. I am a budding Ruby on Rails developer and graphic designer based in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. I have been coding for the past 9 months. Even though I'm fairly new in the coding world, I'm a fast learner hungry for improvement.</p>

        <p>My work ranges from traditional graphic design for posters, brochures, banners and creating responsive web apps. In the near future, I hope to work with tech-driven companies to create beautiful, responsive apps that are futuristic and sustainable. </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-body">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>